    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nI'm looking at developing a mouse hover api, but in order to get the capabilities at an arbitrary location in the buffer one has to either:\n- Manually construct the calls to supporting clients with a custom `lsp.TextDocumentPositionParams` when this whole nice api already exists\n- Save the cursor position, move it quickly, then move it back (not feasible)\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nYou should be able to pass custom positions to these functions",
